er is ordered to divest it, does it just sell the stock back to Musk? What =
price does he pay? Like, 10 bucks, right?)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I guess this thing is closing this week! It is=
 a good thing I have booked a lavish nonrefundable vacation to start Saturd=
ay morning.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"color:=
