</em>except when Elon Musk is the one getting remedied.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But part of me feels like it will never=C2=A0<=
em>really=C2=A0</em>be over. Lots of story lines will continue past closing=
. Maybe CFIUS will make him divest. Maybe he=E2=80=99ll go around syndicati=
