f I were him, I=E2=80=99d go out at $69.42=C2=A0per share and see what happ=
ens; sure <em>he=C2=A0</em>thinks he=E2=80=99s overpaying at $54.20, but wh=
at do <em>they=C2=A0</em>think?) And I am looking forward to the initial pu=
blic offering of Musk Twitter in a couple of years.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also Musk Twitter is going to have to pay some=
thing like <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2947480=
