<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CPumped for our 2023 all hands,=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0tweeted=C2=A0one Twitter employee, referring to a companywide meet=
ing. He included a video of just four people dancing.</p>
</blockquote>
